></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Event/stopImmediatePropagation\"><code>stopImmediatePropagation()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Event/stopPropagation\"><code>stopPropagation()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Páginas relacionadas a DOM</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AbortController\"><code>AbortController</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/AbortSignal\"><code>AbortSignal</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AbstractRange\"><code>AbstractRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Attr\"><code>Attr</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CDATASection\"><code>CDATASection</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/CharacterData\"><code>CharacterData</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Comment\"><code>Comment</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CustomEvent\"><code>CustomEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMError\"><code>DOMError</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/DOMException\"><code>DOMException</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/DOMImplementation\"><code>DOMImplementation</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMParser\"><code>DOMParser</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMPoint\"><code>DOMPoint</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMPointReadOnly\"><code>DOMPointReadOnly</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRect\"><code>DOMRect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMTimeStamp\"><code>DOMTimeStamp</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList\"><code>DOMTokenList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>Document</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>DocumentFragment</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DocumentType\"><code>DocumentType</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLCollection\"><code>HTMLCollection</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/MutationObserver\"><code>MutationObserver</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NamedNodeMap\"><code>NamedNodeMap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NodeIterator\"><code>NodeIterator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/NodeList\"><code>NodeList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/ProcessingInstruction\"><code>ProcessingInstruction</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StaticRange\"><code>StaticRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Text\"><code>Text</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TimeRanges\"><code>TimeRanges</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TreeWalker\"><code>TreeWalker</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/XMLDocument\"><code>XMLDocument</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"><div class=\"notecard deprecated\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>Deprecated:</strong> This feature is no longer recommended. Though some browsers might still support it, it may have already been removed from the relevant web standards, may be in the process of being dropped, or may only be kept for compatibility purposes. Avoid using it, and update existing code if possible; see the <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">compatibility table</a> at the bottom of this page to guide your decision. Be aware that this feature may cease to work at any time.</p></div></div>\n\n<p>O método&nbsp;<strong><code>Event.initEvent()</code></strong>&nbsp;é usado para inicializar&nbsp;o valor de um <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>event</code></a> criado&nbsp;usando <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/createEvent\"><code>Document.createEvent()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</p>\n\n<p>Eventos inicializados desta maneira precisam ter sido&nbsp;criados com o método&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/createEvent\"><code>Document.createEvent()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>. Este método precisar ser chamado para definir o evento antes de ser despachado, usando <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/dispatchEvent\"><code>EventTarget.dispatchEvent()</code></a>. Uma vez despachado, não faz mais nada.</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect3\">\n<p><strong>Não use esse método mais, pois está depreciado.</strong></p>\n\n<p>Ao invés, use construtores de eventos específicos, como&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Event/Event\" title=\"Event()\"><code>Event()</code></a>. A página sobre&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Events/Creating_and_triggering_events\">Criando e disparando eventos</a> detalha mais informações sobre o uso desses eventos.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>event</em>.initEvent(<em>tipo</em>, <em>bubbles</em>, <em>cancelable</em>);</pre>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"tipo\"><em><code>tipo</code></em></dt>\n <dd>É um <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a> definido o tipo do evento.</dd>\n <dt id=\"bolhas\"><em><code>bolhas</code></em></dt>\n <dd>É um <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a> decidindo se o evento precisa ser enviado para cima, na cadeia de eventos ou não.&nbsp;Uma vez definido, a propriedade&nbsp;read-only&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event/bubbles\"><code>Event.bubbles</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> irá informar o seu valor.</dd>\n <dt id=\"cancelable\"><em><code>cancelable</code></em></dt>\n <dd>É um <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a> definindo&nbsp;se o evento pode ser cancelado. Uma vez definido, a propriedade&nbsp;read-only <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event/cancelable\"><code>Event.cancelable</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> will irá informar o seu valor.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Exemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\"><code>// Cria o evento.\nvar event = document.createEvent('Event');\n</code>\n// Cria um evento de clique que borbulha e\n// não pode ser cancelado<code>\nevent.initEvent('click', true, false);\n\n// Escuta este evento.\nelem.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n  // e.target matches elem\n}, false);\n\nelem.dispatchEvent(event);</code>\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificações","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificação</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Estado</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentário</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#dom-event-initevent\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'Event.initEvent()' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Padrão em tempo real</span></td>\n   <td>From <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Events/events.html\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"The 'Document Object Model (DOM) Level 2 Events Specification' specification\" rel=\" noopener\">Document Object Model (DOM) Level 2 Events Specification</a>, deprecated it, superseded by event constructors.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Events/events.html##Events-Event-initEvent\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Document Object Model (DOM) Level 2 Events Specification<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'Event.initEvent()' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">Obsoleto</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect4\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect5\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Edge</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span> [1]</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Edge</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span> [1]</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<p>[1] Antes do Firefox 17, uma chamada a este método depois de despachar o evento gerava uma exceção ao invés de não fazer nada.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>O construtor para usar ao invés deste método descontinuado: <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Event/Event\" title=\"Event()\"><code>Event()</code></a>. Construtores mais específicos também podem ser usados.</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Exemplo","id":"example"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"especificações"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"O método Event.initEvent() é usado para inicializar o valor de um event criado usando Document.createEvent() (en-US).","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Event.initEvent()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"event.initEvent","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"event.initEvent","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Event.initEvent()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"event.initEvent","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Event.initEvent()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Event.initEvent()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/event/initevent","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/event/initevent/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Event","title":"Event"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Event/initEvent","title":"Event.initEvent()"}],"pageTitle":"Event.initEvent() - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}